# GitHub Packages registry mapping for the @facioquo scope (design-system).
# The web/ workspace consumes @facioquo/react-ui + @facioquo/tokens from GitHub
# Packages, so this scope mapping resolves those installs (FAC-2121).
#
# Auth is NOT stored here. pnpm 10+ refuses to expand environment variables in
# credentials read from a committed project .npmrc (a security measure), so the
# token must live in a trusted location:
#   - Local:  pnpm config set "//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken" "$(gh auth token)"
#             (writes to your user ~/.npmrc — never commit a token, LAWS.md §5.1)
#   - CI:     actions/setup-node writes a user-level .npmrc from NODE_AUTH_TOKEN.
@facioquo:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
